</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_217" id="107r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_217_r1l4">Hanſen Erlbecken </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_217_r1l5"> <expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienſt cʒevor / Hans Erlbeck / . Als du vns <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haſt / von 
<del rend="strikethrough">Conrade </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l6">
<del rend="strikethrough">Mollitor / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> B </del> deins <expan>Brüd<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd dem Conrade Mollitor <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l7">dunkt vns etwas vncʒeitlich / daʒ du vns alſo ſchreıbſt / Dann vvir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> darvmb cʒe red geſacʒt / vnd der ſprichet / daʒ Jm von <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Brüd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l10">vaſt vngütlich <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeÿ / . 
<add><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748165282_7320">vnd er ſey </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748167762_7325"><expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Brüd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748169693_7330">nie keins </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748172188_7335"><expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748174243_7340">vns <expan>vvıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748176471_7345">geweſen / </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748178450_7350">So hat auch </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748181788_7355">dein <expan>Brüd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748184534_7360">kein recht an vns </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748186916_7365"><expan>gevord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> / das vvir </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748189443_7370">Jm <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſagt</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576748191563_7375">vnd . </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Doch </del> heſt du <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dein <expan>Brüd<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l12"><expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ıht cʒü <expan>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Darvmb wöllen vvir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l15"><expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt vnuercʒogen <expan>ſlewnig<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen / vvenn wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l17">des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> ſo derſelb vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ıſt / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıȷ̃ . <expan>An<ex>te</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l19">vrbanj / ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_217" id="107r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen Erlbecken </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienst czevor. Hans Erlbeck, als du uns
                                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hast von deins
                                <expan>brüd<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> und dem Conrade Mollitor,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, dunkt uns etwas unczeitlich, daz du uns also
                        schreibst, dann wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> darumb cze red gesaczt und der sprichet, daz
                        im von <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>brüd<ex>er</ex></expan> vast ungütlich
                            <expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey; <add>und er sey
                                    <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>brüd<ex>er</ex></expan> nie keins <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                            vor uns <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> gewesen. So hat auch dein
                                    <expan>brüd<ex>er</ex></expan> kein recht an uns
                                    <expan>gevord<ex>er</ex>t</expan>, das wir im
                                    <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und</add> hest du
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dein <expan>brüd<ex>er</ex></expan> czü
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, iht czü <expan>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        darumb wöllen wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt unverczogen
                            <expan>slewnig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so derselb unser
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ist.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Urbani ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
